data.title: Research Guides at George Washington University
data.meta_description: This guide will provide help on locating both electronic and print resources related on the latest US military base issues in Okinawa.
data.text:
For more information on U.S. military bases in Okinawa, please visit Base-related Data on Okinawa Prefectural Government Washington, D.C. Office homepage. You can browse Historic background of U.S. military bases in Okinawa, Issues stemming from U.S. military bases, U.S. bases and Okinawan economy etc.

For issues of Henoko base construction, please visit a website of Henoko Base Construction Countermeasures Division Executive Office, Okinawa Prefectural Government.
